===Pronoun===
'''everybody'''

# All people.  (''Everybody'' takes a singular verb: ''Is everybody here?'';  ''Everybody has heard of it.'')

====Antonyms====
* [[nobody]], [[no one]]
* Logically [[negates]] to ''not everybody''.

